---
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-cream border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Parents stay in control.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        Review provider profiles, compare region, language, expertise, pricing, and service scope, then choose the support route that fits your family.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center transform transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-brand-trust">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Learn first</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Access evidence-informed resources, understand your child's behavior, and learn what support looks like.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center transform transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-lavender rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-brand-navy">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Compare providers</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Review verified profiles, expertise, service boundaries, and clear pricing options.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center transform transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-brand-trust">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Choose by region</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Find professionals who understand your local context, school systems, and time zones.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center transform transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-lavender rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-brand-navy">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Book when ready</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Schedule your consultation directly through the platform when it feels right for your family.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
